{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_04_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "怜が千紗や雫と話し合うことを約束した、翌朝――",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、聞いて下さい！\n千紗や雫とちゃんと話せました！",
      "startTime": 6.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、それは良かった\nそれで二人はなんて言ってたんだ？",
      "startTime": 11.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "私が謝罪したら、逆に二人から「こっちこそ変な感じに\nなってごめんなさい」って謝られてしまいました",
      "startTime": 19.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスレッスンで私が強く言い過ぎたことも\n二人とも気にしてないからって……",
      "startTime": 27.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "それどころか、これからも遠慮しないで\n厳しく指導してほしいって言われました",
      "startTime": 33,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "怖がられていたらどうしようって\n心配していた私がバカみたいでした",
      "startTime": 38.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "二人は怜のことをよく分かっているからこそ\n厳しいアドバイスを期待しているのかもしれないな",
      "startTime": 44.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……二人の期待に応えて\nこれからもビシビシ厳しく指導していきます！",
      "startTime": 52.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "た、たまには加減してやってくれ",
      "startTime": 55.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "それと、二人も例のSNSの書き込みを\n見たらしくて……",
      "startTime": 61.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "書き込みというと、怜が怖い顔で\n千紗と雫を睨んでいたってやつか",
      "startTime": 66.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "それで二人とも自分のことのように怒ってくれたんです\n「怜ちゃんを悪く言うなんて許せない」って……",
      "startTime": 74.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は「ネットに書き込んだ人は怜ちゃんのことを\n全然分かってない」って怒ってくれて",
      "startTime": 81.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "雫は「クールなのにダンスは情熱的で、時々\n怖いところが怜ちゃんの魅力なのに」って言ってくれて",
      "startTime": 89.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "「時々怖い」は褒め言葉じゃない気がするが……",
      "startTime": 93.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "そこは雫なりの冗談ですよ。もちろん、しっかり\n問い詰めて「時々怖い」は訂正させましたけど",
      "startTime": 101.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（そういうところが怖いのかもな……）",
      "startTime": 106.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、いつも厳しい私が、たまに優しい笑顔を\n見せてくれるギャップが素敵だって……",
      "startTime": 114.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "それを聞いて、ちょっと引っかかるところはあったけど\n……やっぱり嬉しかったんです",
      "startTime": 121.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも私を好きでいてくれてるんだと思ったら\n嬉しくて……でも少し照れくさくて……",
      "startTime": 127.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "つい「ふーん、そう」ってそっけなく答えちゃいました",
      "startTime": 133.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そんな態度を取るから\nクールだと言われるんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 141.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "うう……それを言わないで下さい\n一応自覚はあるんですから",
      "startTime": 147.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夜",
      "startTime": 150.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1133.333333299987,
          "startTime": 152.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 152.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（ん？　レッスン室にまだ誰か残っているのか？）\n（あれは……怜じゃないか）",
      "startTime": 157.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5166.666666699995,
          "startTime": 162.9
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4933.333333399986,
          "startTime": 162.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、{user}さん。お疲れ様です",
      "startTime": 164.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "怜、何をしてるんだ？",
      "startTime": 168.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "ポスターを見ていました\n私達がデビューした時に作ったポスターを……",
      "startTime": 173.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "一目見ただけでみんなの個性が分かる\nいいポスターですよね",
      "startTime": 180.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "さくらは太陽のように明るい笑顔で……\n遙子さんは穏やかで包容力があって……",
      "startTime": 185.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は健気で可愛くて……\n雫の茶目っ気が伝わってきて……",
      "startTime": 192.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "それに比べて、私は硬い気がして……こんな表情じゃ\nクールな印象を持たれるのも仕方ないですね",
      "startTime": 200.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "俺は怜らしくていい表情だと思うが……\nそんなにクールだと思われるのが不満なのか？",
      "startTime": 208.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "あ、誤解しないで下さい\n私はクールって言われるのが嫌な訳じゃないんです",
      "startTime": 214.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "クールとか格好いいとか言われるのは嬉しいんです\n嬉しいんですけど……",
      "startTime": 223.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、私もみんなみたいに明るく可愛く振る舞えたら\n怖いなんて言われることもなかったのかなと思って……",
      "startTime": 230.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "気にしなくても、怜の写真も十分人を引きつける\n魅力があると思うぞ。そうだな……あえて言うなら",
      "startTime": 237.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh012.m4a",
